<span id="freeTextContainer2468669387389442853">picked this up because it popped up on a dark academia list and i couldnt resist. however, even though a large portion of the story involves a boarding school, i wouldnt consider this DA. its definitely more of a gothic ghost story (with a little bit of WWII historical fiction thrown in).<br/><br/>and because of that, it took me some time to warm up to and get invested in school girl chapters set in 1950 because it wasnt quite the DA story i was expecting. i was much more interested in fionas present day </span>
  <span id="freeText2468669387389442853" style="display:none">picked this up because it popped up on a dark academia list and i couldnt resist. however, even though a large portion of the story involves a boarding school, i wouldnt consider this DA. its definitely more of a gothic ghost story (with a little bit of WWII historical fiction thrown in).<br /><br />and because of that, it took me some time to warm up to and get invested in school girl chapters set in 1950 because it wasnt quite the DA story i was expecting. i was much more interested in fionas present day POV, her investigation of the murders, and the unearthing of past secrets.<br /><br />this a very atmospheric and haunting story, a prefect halloween kind of read, packed full of mystery and murder.<br /><br /><b>↠ <i>3.5 stars</i></b></span>
