              <span id="reviewTextContainer2320749737" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17078033113327939806">I hate to give it the “meh” but that’s how this book was for me. The audio is very good though. Most people enjoyed this book way more than I did so don’t take my word for it. <br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/></span>

          </span>
        </div>


